source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000010_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Nald, keeper of the realm of the living.
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000020_NALDTHAL<tab>I am Thal, keeper of the realm of the dead.
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000025_NALDTHAL<tab>Prepare to be judged, children of man.

TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICEHope, is it...? Futile. Utterly futile.
Such feeble light is powerless before darkest despair.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06101_000040_ENDSINGER_NONE_VOICEHoffnung? Habt ihr denn immer noch nicht verstanden?
Kein Licht dringt durch die Schwärze dieser Verzweiflung!
